                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>the above uri:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://www.adobe.com/cgi-bin/redirect?http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-xsl-fo&quot;&gt;http://www.adobe.com/cgi-bin/redirect?http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-xsl-fo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
