&lt;br/&gt;
from the original to &lt;a href=&quot;http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-xsl-fo&quot;&gt;http://lists.w3.org/Archives/Public/www-xsl-fo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
